    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台个人/个体交易管理规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1364438878934904832",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 20pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">您好，为适应业务发展需求，将针对<span style=\"color: #2100ff;\">《</span></span><a href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1090224406216708096\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #2100ff; background: #fbfbfb;\">京东开放平台个人/个体交易管理规则</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #2100ff;\">》</span>进行调整。现进行规则公示，公示期：2026年4月24日- 2026年5月6日，规则预计于 2026年5月7日生效，公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心修订点：</span></strong></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100.0%; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 15.6pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 34.64%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #BFBFBF; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 15.6pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"34%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: center; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心要点</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.06%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #BFBFBF; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 15.6pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"32%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: center; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">修订前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #BFBFBF; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 15.6pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"33%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: center; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">修订后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 75.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 34.64%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 75.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"34%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第四章 第二节的第十八条中增加消费者帮助中心跳转链接</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.06%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 75.0pt;\" width=\"32%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十八条 商家需遵守法律法规、协议、平台规则，为消费者提供&ldquo;售后三包&rdquo;及&ldquo;7天无理由退货&rdquo;等售后服务。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 75.0pt;\" width=\"33%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十八条 商家需遵守法律法规、协议、平台规则（包括但不限于平台在京东用户帮助中心（链接：<span style=\"color: #2100ff;\"><a style=\"color: #2100ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://help.jd.com/user/issue/list-117.html\">https://help.jd.com/user/issue/list-117.html</a></span>）公示的售后服务总则与品类服务细则），为消费者提供&ldquo;售后三包&rdquo;及&ldquo;7天无理由退货&rdquo;等售后服务。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
